'''Eroge''' ({{lang|ja|エロゲ}} or {{lang|ja|エロゲー}}, ''erogē''; {{IPA-ja|eɾoɡe|pron}}; [[ereyga la xardhay]] oo ''erotic game'' {{lang|ja|エロチックゲーム}}, ''erochikku gēmu'')  waa nooc Jabaan ah oo[[Galmada iyo qaawanaanta ee ciyaaraha fiidiyowga|ciyaarta fiidiyowga ee kacsan]]. Sanadkii 1982, [[Koei]]-ga Jabaan, oo ay aasaaseen kooxda ninkeeda iyo xaaskiisa [[Koei|Yoichi]] iyo [[Koei|Keiko Erikawa]] (oo markii dambe loo yaqaanay [[ciyaaraha fiidiyaha istiraatiijiyadeed]]), ayaa sii daayay ciyaartii ugu horreysay ee kombiyuutar ee kacsi leh oo leh sawirro galmo cad ah, ''[[Night Life]]'',<ref name="Retro">[http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/JPNcomputers/Japanesecomputers3.htm Retro Japanese Computers: Gaming's Final Frontier], Hardcore Gaming 101, reprinted from ''[[Retro Gamer]]'', Issue 67, 2009</ref> Dhinaca kale, qorayaasha qaarkood, sida Naoki Miyamoto, ayaa tixgeliyey ''[[:ja:野球拳 (ハドソンのゲーム)|Yakyūken]]'' (1981) loo soo saaray kombiyuutarrada Sharp MZ ee [[Hudson Soft]] si uu u noqdo cayaartii ugu horreysay ee dadka waaweyn ee Jabban.

